    'Features of Java': `public class Main {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        String[] features = {\n            "Platform Independent",\n            "Object-Oriented",\n            "Simple and Familiar",\n            "Secure",\n            "Multithreaded",\n            "Robust and Reliable",\n            "High Performance",\n            "Distributed Computing",\n            "Dynamic and Extensible",\n            "Rich API" \n        };\n        \n        System.out.println("Top 10 Features of Java:");\n        for (int i = 0; i < features.length; i++) {\n            System.out.println((i + 1) + ". " + features[i]);\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n// Output:\n// Top 10 Features of Java:\n// 1. Platform Independent\n// 2. Object-Oriented\n// 3. Simple and Familiar\n// 4. Secure\n// 5. Multithreaded\n// ...`,
